spec_data.Name: pipsi
spec_data.Description:
Pipsi is a wrapper around virtualenv and pip which installs scripts provided
by python packages into separate virtualenvs to shield them from your system
and each other.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 09:43:01 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Wraps pip and virtualenv to install scripts
